text: Rampur is a town located in the Punjab province of Pakistan. It is located in Lahore District at 31°24'0N 73°0'0E with an altitude of 169 metres (557 feet) and lies near to the city of Lahore.Location of Rampur- Falling Rain Genomics Neighbouring settlements include Narwala to the west, Awan Baluch to the north, Jamalpur to the east and Risalewala to the south. ==References== Category:Populated places in Lahore District
title: Rampur, Lahore
